; B--C. Flowers showing the prominent anthers (yellow) of the longest pair of stamens opening at the mouth of corolla tube. 
<taxonomicName authority=": D. Habit" authorityName="D. Habit" box="[758,1133,1929,1953]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Calibrachoa" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="5" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longistyla">
